{"tid":2199120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"19歲醉酒黃絲女疑以胸襲警","createTime":"2020-09-12T02:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T09:16:58.000Z","uid":42188,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a062433be851638233d61cad0eb1cbdb5ada9ec1","tid":2199120,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T02:32:42.000Z","msg":"自稱「忠誠勇毅」的警隊內疑出現色魔。消息指，水警東一名27歲督察，前晚相約19歲中學小師妹聚會，席間師妹酩酊大醉，督察色心頓起，聚會後截的士載師妹返回自己在柴灣區的寓所，途中不斷對無力反抗的師妹施以鹹豬手飽嚐獸慾，抵埗下車時，師妹倒地狂吐，引起巡經現場的警員懷疑，上前了解後揭破事件，以涉嫌非禮將督察拘捕。《蘋果》獲悉後曾向涉案督察的部門主管查詢，對方拒絕回應，要求記者向警察公共關係科查詢，暫時未獲回覆。"},{"pid":"629d5acbc2a20b52b672ac303b7aaf0caf95740a","tid":2199120,"uid":133033,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗 廢狗睇唔過眼職位又高過佢 又有狗乸食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21cc9a6471e846473a55897afbe50f8120c011a","tid":2199120,"uid":169497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"差8歲都可以用中學關係識到<br />\n隻督察lum左幾多年班"},{"pid":"a08c6ddaed219d8298565a142c9d51c16fea45ed","tid":2199120,"uid":361025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:59:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e2e921f521979b54e9618445543bcb0e90446c5","tid":2199120,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a08c6ddaed219d8298565a142c9d51c16fea45ed","tid":2199120,"uid":361025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c21cc9a6471e846473a55897afbe50f8120c011a","tid":2199120,"uid":169497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"差8歲都可以用中學關係識到<br />\n隻督察lum左幾多年班"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:59:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:02:24.000Z","msg":"中大校友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18efe45c1366467b97bc75a62286dabe3b757575","tid":2199120,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:04:07.000Z","msg":"中學聚會仲請曱甴去